Package datastructure

Class SampleAnalysisEntry

java.lang.Object
datastructure.SampleAnalysisEntry
public final class SampleAnalysisEntry
extends java.lang.Object
Internal representation of a sample that is subject to analysis.

Pairs of instances of this class and FeatureAnalysisEntry instances are used internally as so called 'Run entries' to specify a set of analysis tasks, i.e. which sample is analyzed with respect to which specified reference feature.
